r />\n<br />\n主要職責︰<br />\n1. 助理空氣調節督察主要負責安裝、操作及維修空氣調節及冷凝裝置和設備<br />\n2. 提供設計、採購、工程管理及技術顧問服務<br />\n3. 執行法例及提供規管和諮詢服務<br />\n4. 監督承辦商及下屬的工作<br />\n5. 可能會獲調派至其他部門工作，以及可能須不定時／在偏遠地區／在惡劣環境下工作<br />\n6. 有可能執行輪班／上班候命／隨時候召／緊急工作<br />\n7. 穿著制服／保護衣物<br />\n8. 執行其他不時指定的職務<br />\n9. 獲取錄的申請人亦可能要以自願性質執行自行駕車到工作地點的職務（如有需要，部門會提供有關訓練）<br />\n<br />\n聘用條款︰獲取錄的申請人通常會按公務員試用條款受聘三年。通過試用關限後，或可獲考慮按當時適用的長期聘用條款聘用。<br />\n<br />\n月薪︰$28,780至$46,655</span><br />\n<br />\n有冇現職Ching分享下?  好唔好做？ 請咩人多?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:35:11.000Z","msg":"斷估幾好做，主要負責較冷氣<br />\n<br />\nN年前喺法庭做單trial ，個狀話冷氣好凍，個書記係話：咁我打到駐場機電署嚟閂細啲個冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T12:14:50.000Z","msg":"做醫院表示<br />\n醫生投訴冷氣太凍都係call 機電黎較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9e220bb23e2f0f6b718a38b83cb162f97ff295","tid":2052880,"uid":136670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T12:30:10.000Z","msg":"冷氣軍師<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d8ab25255ef5fa1d8002bf56d0cb9b745eb0b0","tid":2052880,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1281614d9065e84b3d646f1c590404ed342a5a75","tid":2052880,"uid":9965,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6d85d53ebabf4698a9c48d40814042ed2b2a0116","tid":2052880,"uid":240733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50831adaa017a472d2c485f48e6ef5d237fdbbd4","tid":2052880,